OL,7,FThe owners of the pub near have been
OL,8,Fordered to rebuild it after the
OL,9,Fhistoric building was destroyed in a
OL,10,Fsuspected arson attack.
OL,12,FOnce known as , the 258-year-old pub
OL,13,Fin Himley was reduced to rubble
OL,14,Ffollowing a fire on 5 August 2023.
OL,16,FIn a post on X, West Midlands Mayor,
OL,17,FAndy Street, praised South Council,
OL,18,Fadding: "An enforcement notice has
OL,19,Fbeen issued against the owners for its
OL,20,Funlawful demolition.
