OL,7,F"They have been ordered to rebuild the
OL,8,Fpub back to what it was before the
OL,9,Ffire - just as we've been lobbying
OL,10,Ffor."
OL,12,FIn a statement, South Staffordshire
OL,13,FCouncil it had "engaged with the
OL,14,Fowners" since the demolition of the
OL,15,FCrooked House pub, "but has reached a
OL,16,Fpoint where formal action is
OL,17,Fconsidered necessary".
