OL,7,FThe enforcement notice served against
OL,8,Fthe owners requires the building to be
OL,9,Frebuilt by February 2027, the council
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FIf work is not completed within the
OL,13,Ftime limit, the local authority can
OL,14,Fprosecute for failure to comply with
OL,15,Fthe notice, it added.
OL,17,FThe owners of the site have 30 days to
OL,18,Fappeal the notice.
