OL,7,FMr Street also thanked the Save the
OL,8,FCrooked House group, which has over
OL,9,F35,000 members, and has been
OL,10,Fcampaigning for the last six months
OL,11,Fsince the historic 18th-century pub
OL,12,Fburned down.
OL,14,FHe said: "It would never have happened
OL,15,Fif it wasn't for the tireless work of
OL,16,Feach and everyone one of you in this
OL,17,Fgroup.
