OL,7,F"What you have done to keep the
OL,8,FCrooked House at the forefront of
OL,9,Fpeople's minds has been exceptional,
OL,10,Fand as Mayor I want to personally
OL,11,Fthank you all.
OL,13,F"I said at the time of the tragedy
OL,14,Fthat the owners had messed with the
OL,15,Fwrong community, and you haven't half
OL,16,Fproved that right."
OL,18,FMr Street had previously called for
OL,19,Fthe pub to be "rebuilt brick by brick"
