OL,7,FSupporters argued that restoring the
OL,8,Fpub to its former glory was essential
OL,9,Ffor preserving the cultural and
OL,10,Fhistorical heritage of the area.
OL,12,FAn initiative was launched following
OL,13,Fthe destruction of the iconic inn to
OL,14,Fhelp protect historic and cherished
OL,15,Fpubs in the area.
OL,17,FWest Midlands Combined Authority
OL,18,F(WMCA) submitted five local pubs for
OL,19,FGrade II listed status.
